/target
# Legacy single-deployment dir from the pre-burrowctl era. Kept for
# transition; remove after the legacy `gen-embed*` recipes go.
/burrow-configs
# burrowctl deployments. Everything is gitignored by default — `dev`
# specs are typically scratch and the spec itself contains addressing
# info we don't need to commit. Once we have an example/template
# spec worth versioning, allow-list it explicitly via `!deployments/example/spec.toml`.
/deployments/
